	function...
	(xml_write_calculation): ...extracted from here.
	(gnm_cellregion_to_xml): Call xml_write_date_conventions_as_attr
	if we have a sheet.

	* src/clipboard.c (cellregion_to_string): Use the value format
	  when appropriate.

