	* */*.c: No need to reset errno before go_strtod and gnm_strto.

	* src/xml-sax-read.c (xml_sax_double): Don't use g_strtod.  We do
	not need or want dual-locale semantics.
	(gnm_xml_attr_double): Ditto.

