	* src/mathfunc.c (gcd): Remove.
	* src/sheet-view.c (sv_get_control): Remove.
	* src/stf-parse.c (stf_parse_options_remove_line_terminator): Remove.
	* src/value.c (value_new_error_RECALC, value_array_resize): Remove.

